history.text: I thought Patty Jenkins directed the movie amazing. The cinematography was so visually stunning!
yes it looked amazing
the cast was wonderful too
Do you like superhero movies normally?
yes but normally the marvel ones
I agree about the cast! I thought Chris Pine was especially great and Gal made a fantastic Diana!
yep the story was good also
I loved that it was an origin story, especially after her debut in Batman v Superman!
yes and i hope we see more wonder women movies
and the reviews are good
I agree! Especially with Patty Jenkins directing again.
yes that makes for a soild movie
I was really surprised by the rating on Rotten Tomatoes. It seems like everyone enjoys the movie!
yes normally it does just okay
I read the CinemaScore was an A. It seems like both critics and fans really enjoyed it!
what do you think about the past for wonder woman
Her past? I think she has a great origin story! I loved that they showed her growing up in Themyscira and how she became Wonder Woman! What was your favorite part?
i guess the fight scenes
You mean when Diana was training with Hippolyta? I thought it was fantastic to show her training and becoming stronger and how that shaped her into being the superhero she is now!
yes it was really great
I thought the scene where she rescued Steve was a great idea, as it showed a little more tenderness after all the fight training!
yes i like that the war was going on in all of this it added tp the story
I agree! I thought it was a great use of history to include the war and have Steve be a pilot!
yes i agree
I especially loved seeing Diana arm herself with the sword and the lasso, ready for battle! Such an iconic moment, I think.
yes but i was sad that steve died
It was so sad! But I think it really helped show Diana that humans have good in them and that she needed to do good, just like Steve did.
yes that's true
I think it was great they tied it into the end of Batman v Superman, where Bruce sent Diana the file containing the photo of her and Steve!
yes that was cool
i had fun talking bye
